1 - Download and Install VirtualBox on your local machine.
        - download from->  https://www.virtualbox.org/
 
2 - Start and open Virtual Box on your local machine
        - Click the New icon (blue sunnish looking icon):
        - Fill in the dialog that pops up
            My Choices:
                Name:               Ubuntu
                Machine Folder:     leave at default
                Type:               Linux
                Version:            Ubuntu (64-bit)
        - Click Next
        - Set Memory Size on this Dialog
            My Choice:              2048 MB
        - Click Next
        - Select Hard Disk
            My Choice:              Default
        - Click Create
        - Select Hard Disk File Type
            My Choice:              Default
        - Click Next
        - Create Virtual Hard Disk
            My Choice:              Default (dynamically allocated)
        - Click Next
        - File Location and size:
            My Choice:              Default (10GB)
        - Click Create
        
3 - Start New VM and Install Ubuntu
        - Select your new machine on the left side of screen
        - Click Start (green arrow point left on icon menu)
        - Select Startup Disk:
            ubuntu-18.04.3-desktop-amd64.iso (1.94GB)
        - Wait 1-2 minutes
        - On Welcome screen, select your language (English)
            - click Install Ubuntu
        - Select your language
            - My Choice:        English (US)
            - Click Continue
        - On updates and other software
            - Choose Normal Installation
            - Choose Download updates while installing Ubuntu
            - Click  Continue
        - Installation Type
            - Erase disk and install Ubuntu
            - Click Install Now
            - Click Continue in the popup dialog to confirm
        - Where are you ( Choose: New York or where you are ).
            - Click Continue
        - Complete the next dialog
            - Your Name:     jeff
            - Computer Name: Ubuntu
            - username:      jeff
            - password:      jeff
            - choose         Log in automatically
        - Wait for: 5 minuts
            - reboot computer when asked.